make the ultimate amends.

34:11.717 --> 34:13.554
I gotta kill myself.

34:14.179 --> 34:16.764
Only problem is I can'T.

34:17.349 --> 34:18.391
I'm not drinkin' no more,

34:18.433 --> 34:21.770
