34:22.603 --> 34:24.857
Tom,do another shot.

34:25.148 --> 34:26.984
Te-teddy,I...

34:27.067 --> 34:30.571
Do another shot now.

34:39.996 --> 34:42.541
So I figure I'd put a bullet in this gun

34:43.167 --> 34:45.502
