35:02.060 --> 35:05.647
I will rip your freakin'
head out of your goddamn neck!

35:07.900 --> 35:10.402
Tom,drink.

35:20.329 --> 35:22.414
Did you drink much before I showed up?

35:23.624 --> 35:25.167
Little more than usual.

35:25.250 --> 35:26.502
Good.

35:26.585 --> 35:28.295
This should work out great,then.

35:29.463 --> 35:30.339
You feelin' a little lightheaded?

35:30.380 --> 35:31.340
Yeah.

35:31.423 --> 35:32.883
Perfect.

35:33.759 --> 35:36.303
You remember the name bubba cohen?

35:36.887 --> 35:39.097
Friend of your old
man's back in the day.

35:39.473 --> 35:44.895
Big guy,dumber than drywall,got
mobbed up around age 19,

35:45.312 --> 35:48.273
got a job as a leg-breaker
for the local guinea mob.

35:49.399 --> 35:52.152
