36:04.248 --> 36:05.916
So much for bubba,huh?

36:06.124 --> 36:08.418
You'd think so,but he didn't die.

36:09.127 --> 36:12.130
Guy was an animal,huge,size of a shed,

36:12.165 --> 36:14.007
but that ain't what saved him.

36:14.049 --> 36:15.342
On the night in question,

36:15.425 --> 36:19.721
