36:29.022 --> 36:31.483
You see,that's my problem.

36:31.567 --> 36:36.155
If I wanna off myself,I gotta drink my
weight in booze just to pull the trigger.

36:36.405 --> 36:39.324
Then I'll be so shitfaced,I
won't be able to kick the bucket.

36:39.408 --> 36:43.829
Now,I got this gun here with
5 empty chambers and one round,

36:44.121 --> 36:46.874
so the odds are stacked
pretty much in my favor.

36:47.332 --> 36:49.710
But why don't we all
just leave it to fate?

36:50.419 --> 36:52.087
You wanna do the honors,tom?

36:53.505 --> 36:56.049
