37:21.658 --> 37:22.993
Ok,ok!

37:23.076 --> 37:25.120
I said I had one round in that gun.

37:25.204 --> 37:26.663
Sorry,2.

37:26.997 --> 37:30.083
But this,this is a glock 17.

37:30.334 --> 37:35.214
This has got 19 rounds,so
that means I got 16 left.

37:35.255 --> 37:37.508
And by the by,just so you know,

37:37.549 --> 37:40.761
I'm sober as a judge,in
case anybody's wonderin'.

37:40.928 --> 37:42.846
