there so I could see 'em.

37:51.438 --> 37:52.564
That's it.

37:53.690 --> 37:55.150
All of 'em.

37:57.319 --> 37:59.321
'Cause I want you
guys to know somethin'.

37:59.613 --> 38:01.031
